    en: 'This task is about the stack. \
       \
      Your task is to implement a stack supporting the operations StackPush, StackPop, StackEmpty and StackPeek. \
      Then, you should test your implementation of the stack. \
      The comment in the given code conatins a list of directions that will lead your owl to the goal. \
      Your task is to push each direction onto the stack and then pop the directions one by one to get your owl to the goal using your stack implementation.',
